-- U.A.E. Market Regulator Issues Investment Law, Alrroya Says
-- B y   Z a h r a   H a n k i r
-- 2012-07-25T07:42:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-25/u-a-e-market-regulator-issues-investment-law-alrroya-says.html
The United Arab Emirates Securities
and Commodities Authority issued a decision stipulating rules
for investment funds in the Persian Gulf country as it seeks to
boost liquidity in the markets,  Alrroya reported .  The decision will increase transparency of  fund management ,
Alrroya said, citing the market regulator chief executive
officer Abdullah al Turaifi.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zahra Hankir in Dubai at 
 zhankir@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
